				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>You certainly do have a way with these word thingies, Doc!<br />
Plz to save some for rest of us? 😉</p>
<p>Despite the eerie empty house, I didn&#8217;t get the suicide-y vibes.<br />
More like a walking away from a shell.</p>
<p>Language, as usual, beautiful: &#8220;elegant in glossy suits&#8221; and &#8220;skirts flapping in the wind&#8221; being particular favourites for words and images.<br />
Also dug the &#8220;sudden, urgent rush&#8221; of the unexpected transformation.</p>
<p>Very wispy, lovely, piece of writing.</p>
